Class TheActualClient

java.lang.Object
  edu.iastate.cs309.client.TheActualClient
All Implemented Interfaces:
Client
public class TheActualClient
extends Object
implements Client

TheActualClient is an implementation of a Client. It gets and displays information in an instance of MainGUi. It must always be linked to a MainGui

Author:
Justin Nelson
